    "title": "Job Opening Teacher at IIT Madras",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at IIT Madras. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Teacher to strengthen our Varanasi-based team.\n\nAbout IIT Madras:\nIIT Madras is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IIT Madras!",
